{"tid":1525802,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[警世文]主仼務同副本係咪唔識分呀","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:48:35.000Z","uid":28942,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1b53bc052a030dbaf62a2c5c9d10ea79880f08","tid":1525802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:04:50.000Z","msg":"而係咪主任務同副本都唔識分？<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門全部都話要搞狗鐵，依家唔係話唔搞得，但係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定要對準政權！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n政權、清算、文宣&mdash;&mdash;缺一不可，但有先後緩急。<br />\n<br />\n清算就一定要清算，無論係黨鐵、藍絲、黑警定係建制派議員都一定要清算。<br />\n<br />\n如果過分集中於清算行動，政權只會無動於衷而且觀感亦都唔好。<br />\n<br />\n我並唔係話不能夠同時進行，但唔該分一分輕重。<br />\n<br />\n我相信香港人同前線嘅智慧，好似尋日西環屯重兵，冇人走去嗰度。我哋贏係贏在人多同我哋嘅流動性。<br />\n唔該各位認真考慮一下，應唔應該忍一忍手，留返我哋嘅精神體力做一啲對政權有直接影響嘅東西。<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，如果要抗爭，就要下下踢佢春袋！"},{"pid":"3a1610c681e0b08550e0e488a7e9c68b80662879","tid":1525802,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:05:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試分辨以上事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月，機場見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c8483c31c1d0077b44413c147768090252786583","tid":1525802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"df7b87bfdc008747a7107d8a6200a7f00fb57c74","tid":1525802,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:05:51.000Z","msg":"熱烈宣傳中共誠信破產，殘害人民<br />\n<br />\n中共最怕香港成為「反共基地」<br />\n<br />\n中共最怕持續性抗爭<br />\n<br />\n中共最怕外國勢力<br />\n<br />\n覺得岩、有value就做啦<br />\n遊行、連儂、傳單、網絡戰<br />\n<br />\n自由無罪，造反有理<br />\n<br />\nBe water 不被捕 不分化 不割席"},{"pid":"0352c513203f27aa8c09c5f7ef3c092add7f0f82","tid":1525802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:06:40.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"b4247ae9b25864fa9f75e800ab3f9304c4e461e7","tid":1525802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:06:55.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"94c058017566d8f361a3e3428787dcdd80fd74d0","tid":1525802,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:07:55.000Z","msg":"等車入機場果陣幫手做下<br />\n<br />\n就杜浩成法官作出有罪假定及煽動他人侵權之言論作出投訴（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1521682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1521682</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0d9e7bddba927ebab8551f7c289da8fa82cc9fb2","tid":1525802,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"輸出革命！香港獨立！"},{"pid":"6d0424c70ef8b0da8e601b48fab1065c38549e55","tid":1525802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"9de6bf414c6708f2721531f5d3f405126874714d","tid":1525802,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲垃圾說話<br />\n點樣推翻政府唔打仗?"},{"pid":"2d063669aa5299d0e0e7975015780a04f4917f6b","tid":1525802,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9de6bf414c6708f2721531f5d3f405126874714d","tid":1525802,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:11:40.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲垃圾說話<br />\n點樣推翻政府唔打仗?"},"citedBy":